{{Infobox Criminal organization | name = Red Wa | founded = | founding location = [[Myanmar]] | ethnicity = [[Va people|Va]] | territory = [[Southeast Asia]] | criminal activities = [[drug trafficking]], [[arms trafficking]], [[counterfeiting]], [[extortion]], [[Truck hijacking|hijacking]], [[kidnapping]] and [[murder]] | allies = [[Triad (underground society)|Triads]], local [[Han Chinese|Chinese]] criminals }}
The '''Red Wa''' is the most powerful organized crime gang in Thailand. The Red Wa come from [[Burma]] and they are associated with the [[United Wa State Army]]. They are composed of people from the [[Va people|Va]] ethnic group and they work together with Chinese organized criminals in the drug trade. The Red Wa control the [[methamphetamine]] trade in Thailand and neighboring countries<ref>http://www.chiangmaipost.net/a371-police-seize-b500m-drugs-haul</ref> and are also known for being involved in the trafficking and sale of other drugs, mainly heroin.<ref>http://www.dvb.no/news/thai-heroin-haul-%E2%80%98traces-back-to-wa%E2%80%99/14452</ref> Although they primarily focus on [[drug trafficking]], groups associated with the [[United Wa State Army]] have also been involved in other crimes in order to protect their territory.<ref>http://www.intelasia.net/burma-is-key-to-ending-regional-drug-trafficking-233353</ref>
